---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use | SMS API Compare"
  description="Terms and conditions for using SMS API Compare website."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        By accessing and using SMS API Compare ("the Site"), you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use the Site.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Use of Content</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        All content on SMS API Compare is provided for <strong>informational purposes only</strong>. The comparisons, pricing data, and recommendations on this site do not constitute financial, legal, or professional advice. You should conduct your own research and consult with appropriate professionals before making purchasing decisions based on information found on this site.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Accuracy of Information</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information about SMS API providers, including pricing, features, and capabilities. However, providers may change their pricing, features, or terms at any time without notice. We make no guarantees that the information on this site is complete, current, or error-free. Always verify pricing and feature details directly with the provider before making a commitment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Affiliate Links Disclosure</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        SMS API Compare may contain affiliate links to SMS API providers and related services. When you click on these links and make a purchase or sign up for a service, we may receive a commission at no additional cost to you. These affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial content, comparisons, or rankings. We are committed to providing honest and unbiased information regardless of affiliate partnerships.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        All content on SMS API Compare, including text, graphics, logos, and design, is the property of SMS API Compare or its content creators and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without prior written consent. Provider names, logos, and trademarks mentioned on this site belong to their respective owners.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        SMS API Compare and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Site or reliance on any information provided. This includes, but is not limited to, damages resulting from choosing a provider based on our comparisons, pricing inaccuracies, or service disruptions. The Site is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Use at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Your continued use of the Site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised terms. We encourage you to review these terms periodically.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        If you have questions about these Terms of Use, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:contact@smsapicompare.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@smsapicompare.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
